dapest next month would send her to this summer's Games as one of the favourites for gold.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9831541691596752, \"rank\": 0.017134475305857242, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A repeat performance\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 286}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"the favourites\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 372}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breakdancing, or 'breaking' as the sport is officially called, will make its Olympic debut in the French capital.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9896908162289869, \"rank\": 0.010328456554641069, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am old, but I do not feel too much old,\\\" Fukushima told AFP in English after her victory in China at the weekend.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 543, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"score\": 0.5832848883832169, \"rank\": 0.7144000471571312, \"text\": \"Fukushima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\"}, {\"begin\": 558, \"end\": 561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\"