m\": \"her age\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"her first and last shot\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a new thing for us, for the Olympics, so I am really happy to be in this process,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new thing\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan has long been a breakdancing powerhouse, with three Japanese B-girls and one B-boy making it onto the podium in Shanghai on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1569, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9371999060515976, \"rank\": 0.05039921246353543, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1627, \"end\": 1635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9963375324683371, \"rank\": 0.003251848793090578, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1687, \"end\": 1695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9999784338915046, \"rank\": 1.182512225003286e-05, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a breakdancing powerhouse\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"one B-boy\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1705}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the young people are very strong,\\\" Fukushima said of her teammates.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1748, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"score\": 0.5832848883832169, \"rank\": 0.7144000471571312, \"text\": \"Fukushima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the young people\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1779}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not only winning, we enjoy this moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For years Fukushima balanced her day job as a teacher with her role as a member of a dance crew based in Kyoto.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"score\": 0.5832848883832169, \"rank\": 0.7144000471571312, \"text\": \"Fukushima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fukushima_nuclear_disaster\"}, {\"begin\": 1935, \"end\": 1940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyoto\", \"score\": 0.9999961117260333, \"rank\": 3.167773841884069e-06, \"text\": \"Kyoto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyoto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyoto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"her day job\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"her role\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1909}, {\"ngram\": \"a dance crew\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has cut back on her teaching duties in recent months, telling AFP that she is now \\\"more focused on dancing\\\".\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2009, \"end\": 2012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999316041818, \"rank\": 6.764920139200563e-08, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her teaching duties\", \"from\": 1963, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"recent months\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"dancing\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she carves out time to give dance classes to young children, whom she hopes will bring the fledgling sport to greater heights.\", \"from\": 2057, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"dance classes\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"young children\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the fledgling sport\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"greater heights\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everywhere I go I see many kids interested in breaking... and for us it's really happy.\\\"\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2278, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many kids\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2221}, {\"ngram\": \"breaking\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the sidelines of the Shanghai qualifier, dozens of children practised breakdancing moves at a public workshop intended to popularise the sport, while the Japanese team warmed up nearby.\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\"